dct_description_sm: Oriented with north toward right of sheet.
Latitudinal and longitudinal lines along margins.
Key in lower left: Expositio Verborum Hibernicorum.
Decorative cartouches, shield, ships, sea monsters.
From Ortelius’ Theatrum Orbis Terrarum, Antwerp: Vrients, 1612.
